        "Params": "{3: 'In that haunting dream, she returned to her hometown, just the same as the present moment. To her dismay, some of her trusted comrades had betrayed their cause, leaving everyone else hopelessly trapped amidst a relentless snowstorm and the menacing onslaught of the Corrupted waves.'}"
